# Claude Code: everything under .claude/ is personal/machine-local runtime state
# by default (locks, checkpoints, mailbox, routines, daemon/registry state, …).
# Only the curated dirs/files below are un-ignored and shared with the team —
# opt a new one in by adding a `!` line once the team has agreed to adopt it.
.claude/*
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/rules/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/output-styles/
!.claude/settings.json
# Personal overrides live outside .claude/ (or as the ignored settings.local.json);
# never commit these even though they sit in an otherwise-shared tree.
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/settings.local.json

# Ignore Jetbrains related files
.idea/

# Ignore MacOS related files
.DS_Store
topazerrors.log

# Playwright acceptance-test artifacts
acceptance/playwright-report/
acceptance/test-results/
acceptance/.vscode-test/

# Refactoring design / TDD stage docs — local working notes, kept out of the repo
gs-src/refactoring/design/
